lts datacenter\n!\ninterface lo\n no shutdown\n ! no ip address\n ipv6 address 2001:db8:1:2::1/64\n!\ninterface eth1\n no shutdown\n description p1 -> dut\n ! no ip address\n ipv6 address 2001:db8:3::2/64\n ipv6 nd ra-interval 5\n no ipv6 nd suppress-ra\n!\ndo write\nCONFIG\nvtysh -f /tmp/config\n!\nexit 0\n"
